quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  29,46,"Onon gom…óim…ìe …ìen, wata on yewtir Alyahuuda e Annasaara wennjirgol …ìe, si wanaa noone …ìur…óo mo∆¥∆¥ude on; on woni noddirgol …ìe waaju e hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói, si wanaa hara ko …ìen too√±ir…ìe e ma…ì…ìe sattere-noppi e mawnitaare, …ìe …ìannginani on hare. ∆Åen …óon, ha…ìee …ìe haa …ìe silma maa …ìe jonnira sagalle …óen junngu e junngo hara ko …ìe jaasu…ìe. Wi'anon Alyahuuda e Annasaara: Men gom…óinii nden Alqur'aanaare nde Alla jippini e amen, e …óen …óe O jippini e moo…óon immorde e Tawreeta e Linjiila. Rewetee…óo amen On e rewtee…óo mon On ko gooto Mo alaa kafidii…óo e Reweede Mun e Jeygol Mun e timmal Mun. Menen on, ko Kanko tun men jebbilantoo."
  29,47,"Ko wano Men jippinirnoo Defte …óen non e …ìen adi- adinoo…ìe ma, Men jippiniri Alqur'aana e maa…óa. Yoga e …ìee janngoo…ìe Tawreeta, wano ‚ÄòAbduLlaah ibn Salaam, hino gom…óiniri nde sabu ko nde joopa joopaa fii mun kon ka defte ma…ì…ìe. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen …óen, si wanaa heefer…ìe …ìen woowu…ìe yeddugol goonga ko o fee√±i woo."
  29,48,"A wonaano an Nulaa…óo, hi…óa janngaynoo deftere woo, ado Alque'aana. A wonaano kadi windiray-noo…óo huunde √±aamo maa ngon; tawde a janngaano. Sinno hi…óa janngunoo waawu…óaa winndugol, pellet, yim…ìe majju…ìe …ìen sikkitotono Annabaaku maa ngun, …ìe dallinora wonnde ko e defte adinoo…óe …óen eggu-…óaa."
  29,49,"Si ko woni fii Alqur'aana jippinaande nden e maa…óa, ko nde Aayeeje …ìanngu…óe e …ìer…ìe …ìen okkaa…ìe ganndal e gom…óim…ìe …ìen. Yeddataa Aayeeje Amen …óen, si wanaa …ìen too√±ir…ìe ko'e-mun yeddugol Alla e sirkangol Mo."
  29,50,"Sirkoo…ìe …ìen wi'i: Hanno jippinee e Muhammadu maandeeji immorde ka Joomi makko sugu …óen jippinoo…óe e Nulaa…ìe adinoo…ìe mo …ìen? Maakan an Nulaa…óo: Anndee maandeej …óin, ko e Juu…óe Alla woni. Himo jippina …ói nde O muuyi woo, wanaa min …óum wonani. Min on, ko mi jertinoowo on e lepte Alla …óen, …ìanngu…óo jertinol."
  29,51,"Kere yonaa…ìe …ìee lanndii…ìe maandeeji wonnde Men jippinii e maa…óa an Nulaa…óo, Alqur'aana hinde janngee e ma…ì…ìe? Wonii e Alqur'anaa jippinaande nden e ma…ì…ìe, yurmeende e waaju wonannde yim…ìe gom…óinoo…ìe; ko kam…ìe woni ko nafitorta ko woni e mayre. Men jippinanii …ìe ko …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude ko …ìe lanndii kon haa hewta ko jippinanoo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen kon."
  29,52,"Maakan …ìe an Nulaa…óo: Alla yonii seedee goongugol ko mi addi kon, e wonnde on fennii …óum. Himo anndi kon ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi, huunde suu…óaaki Mo e …óin …ói…ói. ∆Åen non gom…óim…ìe meere immorde e rewoo…ìe ko wanaa Alla …ìen, …ìe yeddi Alla hanndu…óo e reweede On tun, ko …ìen woni sooyu…ìe …ìen; sabu ko…ìe wa…ótitiri keeferaaku ngun kon gom…óinal ngal."